summary: Unravel the perverted secrets of Club Obos in this fully voiced quest line.
descriptionHtml:
Unravel the perverted secrets of Club Obos in this fully voiced quest line. Start the quest by talking to Vetle the Argonian who lives in the basement of Olava\'s house in Whiterun (enter through the trapdoor behind the house).

FEATURES:

- Fully voiced
- Books to read
- Obscure characters
- 2 small dungeons
- A treasure hunt
- Murder old ladies for profit
author: Merte
